1
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah!</font>

2
00:00:10,810 --> 00:00:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just like Leviathan!</font>

3
00:00:13,960 --> 00:00:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So there were others?</font>

4
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have your own will, 
too, don't you?</font>

5
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:22,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

6
00:00:24,980 --> 00:00:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obey me!</font>

7
00:00:43,850 --> 00:00:46,060
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fffdfe">Fire</font></b></font></font></font>

8
00:00:43,850 --> 00:00:46,060
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fffdfe">Water</font></b></font></font></font>

9
00:00:44,440 --> 00:00:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

10
00:00:47,650 --> 00:00:49,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You tamed it?</font>

11
00:00:49,530 --> 00:00:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

12
00:00:52,030 --> 00:00:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? So quickly?</font>

13
00:00:54,070 --> 00:00:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have known.</font>

14
00:00:58,070 --> 00:01:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brilliant judgment.</font>

15
00:01:00,830 --> 00:01:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You chose Luthier without 
the slightest hesitation.</font>

16
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luthier...</font>

17
00:01:06,270 --> 00:01:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems to possess a 
great deal of power.</font>

18
00:01:09,230 --> 00:01:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to test it? 
I will prepare a target.</font>

19
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that won't be necessary.</font>

20
00:01:15,450 --> 00:01:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Your eyes tell me you 
have some sort of plan.</font>

21
00:01:22,940 --> 00:01:24,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, here I go.</font>

22
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah...</font>

23
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right.</font>

24
00:01:41,600 --> 00:01:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just as I predicted.</i></font>

25
00:01:43,110 --> 00:01:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Leviathan is just slightly more powerful.</i></font>

26
00:01:47,330 --> 00:01:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't feel hot...</font>

27
00:01:49,020 --> 00:01:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at the ground.</font>

28
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leviathan is keeping it in check 
to prevent the heat from escaping.</font>

29
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've tamed it to that point 
already? Astounding...</font>

30
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I formally entrust Luthier to you, Noah.</font>

31
00:02:03,030 --> 00:02:07,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use it for the good of the empire.</font>

32
00:02:07,470 --> 00:02:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall.</font>

33
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,540
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

34
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,540
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#051529">m 0 0 l 235 0 l 225 8 l 235 15 l 18 15 l 30 8 l 18 0</font></font>

35
00:03:41,710 --> 00:03:45,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Meeres Empire holds dominion 
over a vast amount of land.</i></font>

36
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:50,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Its highest ruler, the emperor, 
governs all of its affairs.</i></font>

37
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This includes domestic affairs, 
such as law and finance,</i></font>

38
00:03:53,410 --> 00:03:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and diplomatic affairs, such as mediating
disputes and international negotiations.</i></font>

39
00:03:58,830 --> 00:04:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The emperor also mediates in the 
imperial family's private matters,</i></font>

40
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>known as internal law 
and internal affairs.</i></font>

41
00:04:09,300 --> 00:04:14,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A personal declaration from the emperor's 
younger brother, Graeme Ararat?</i></font>

42
00:04:14,730 --> 00:04:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Graeme's son... my nephew.</font>

43
00:04:18,830 --> 00:04:22,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He ruled over his domain 
with extreme tyranny,</font>

44
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:26,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now, in a drunken stupor,
killed someone during an argument.</font>

45
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That alone is a serious crime,</font>

46
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:34,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but his father, Graeme, has declared 
a lack of oversight on his part</font>

47
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:37,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and personally offered to pay a fine.</font>

48
00:04:38,010 --> 00:04:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, under imperial law, 
Prince Graeme has committed no crime.</font>

49
00:04:43,350 --> 00:04:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just as a child is not responsible 
for paying his parents' debts,</font>

50
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:49,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a parent is not responsible 
for his child's crimes.</font>

51
00:04:50,230 --> 00:04:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said as much.</font>

52
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose he's hoping 
to buy peace of mind.</font>

53
00:04:55,410 --> 00:04:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thirty thousand rean...</i></font>

54
00:04:57,610 --> 00:05:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's about 250 times the average 
yearly income in the capital.</i></font>

55
00:05:01,210 --> 00:05:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a significant sum.</i></font>

56
00:05:03,450 --> 00:05:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Noah?</font>

57
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We cannot collect a fine from someone 
who has committed no crime.</font>

58
00:05:10,190 --> 00:05:13,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if he has offered to pay it himself.</font>

59
00:05:13,450 --> 00:05:16,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then shall we revise the law</font>

60
00:05:16,050 --> 00:05:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to institutionalize voluntary 
payment of fines?</font>

61
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:24,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The national treasury is 
in chronic dire straits.</font>

62
00:05:24,050 --> 00:05:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disaster relief and suppression 
of revolts do cost money.</font>

63
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:33,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's why he's hoping to bring 
in incidental income like this.</i></font>

64
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't blame him, but...</i></font>

65
00:05:36,740 --> 00:05:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we were to set such a precedent,</font>

66
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">people would get the idea that they can 
get out of any crime just by paying money.</font>

67
00:05:44,640 --> 00:05:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would make the prevention 
of crime more difficult.</font>

68
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And since only the wealthy 
would be able to afford the fines—</font>

69
00:05:52,850 --> 00:05:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">major merchants, nobles, and 
government officials—</font>

70
00:05:55,790 --> 00:05:59,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it would eventually breed 
corruption in our government.</font>

71
00:06:01,410 --> 00:06:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The empire's lack of funds 
is a grave problem,</font>

72
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:08,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it is one we should resolve 
through respectable means.</font>

73
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True. You were right to admonish me.</font>

74
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To celebrate your wisdom, the likes 
of which we rarely see in a ruler,</font>

75
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hereby name you my premier advisor.</font>

76
00:06:31,870 --> 00:06:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Advisor?</i></font>

77
00:06:33,050 --> 00:06:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an honorary post.</font>

78
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dislike it?</font>

79
00:06:38,190 --> 00:06:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, I have a proposal.</font>

80
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not allow people to pay money</font>

81
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:46,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">not to escape punishment, 
but to attain honor?</font>

82
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, those who donate 
a thousand rean to the empire</font>

83
00:06:52,080 --> 00:06:55,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">may be granted honorary knighthood.</font>

84
00:06:55,950 --> 00:07:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will need caveats to ensure it 
can't be abused to gain real power,</font>

85
00:07:00,210 --> 00:07:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but many would love to be granted such 
an honor by Your Majesty personally.</font>

86
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When humans...</i></font>

87
00:07:07,730 --> 00:07:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>come into possession of more 
money than they can use,</i></font>

88
00:07:11,790 --> 00:07:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>they begin to desire honor more 
than physical possessions.</i></font>

89
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. What a brilliant idea.</font>

90
00:07:18,890 --> 00:07:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You impress me, Noah.</font>

91
00:07:20,410 --> 00:07:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cruz, summon Oscar. At once.</font>

92
00:07:23,870 --> 00:07:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

93
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty.</font>

94
00:07:27,550 --> 00:07:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've just remembered some unfinished 
business at the Ministry of Law.</font>

95
00:07:30,790 --> 00:07:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to take my leave.</font>

96
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This needs to stop.</i></font>

97
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it goes any further, I'll be 
intruding on Oscar's dominion.</i></font>

98
00:07:39,130 --> 00:07:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are clever, Noah.</font>

99
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:51,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are all astonished by the 
amazing feat you've performed.</font>

100
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's you, Sheezu.</font>

101
00:07:53,190 --> 00:07:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They can't comprehend how the ground 
could simply melt away like that.</font>

102
00:07:58,310 --> 00:08:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone has fallen into 
it trying to find out.</font>

103
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How careless.</font>

104
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

105
00:08:06,630 --> 00:08:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To treat the one who fell.
Spare no expense.</font>

106
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Your Highness.</font>

107
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this?</font>

108
00:08:12,340 --> 00:08:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah.</font>

109
00:08:14,890 --> 00:08:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something I had delivered 
for the Sixteenth Prince.</font>

110
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:19,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is only three,</font>

111
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he likes to make 
rhinoceros beetles fight.</font>

112
00:08:23,330 --> 00:08:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh...</font>

113
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Making them fight, eh?</i></font>

114
00:08:30,630 --> 00:08:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you up to it?</font>

115
00:08:37,330 --> 00:08:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leviathan. Luthier.</font>

116
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They really do have</i></font>

117
00:08:49,660 --> 00:08:52,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>all the techniques of their 
past owners engraved in them.</i></font>

118
00:08:53,690 --> 00:08:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm learning a lot watching them, but...</i></font>

119
00:08:58,670 --> 00:09:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The difference in strength is clear.</i></font>

120
00:09:00,950 --> 00:09:02,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

121
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Please pardon my intrusion!</font>

122
00:09:07,010 --> 00:09:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was magic, wasn't it?</font>

123
00:09:08,790 --> 00:09:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to see it again?</font>

124
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I?!</font>

125
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They seem up for it.</font>

126
00:09:16,820 --> 00:09:19,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Unlike my faithful Leviathan,</i></font>

127
00:09:19,170 --> 00:09:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Luthier seems quite competitive.</i></font>

128
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Learning their moves like this 
might make me stronger, too.</i></font>

129
