00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:34,460
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#8f8570">m 0 0 l 258 0 258 21 0 21</font></font>

131
00:09:32,250 --> 00:09:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My level went up!</i></font>

132
00:09:34,460 --> 00:09:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could it be...</i></font>

133
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Leviathan has won every 
battle so far, but now...</i></font>

134
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done. You've come into your own.</font>

135
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:56,320
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#fcfdfc"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Fire</font></b></font></font>

136
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:56,320
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#fcfdfc"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Water</font></b></font></font>

137
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:56,320
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#fcfdfc"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Wind</font></b></font></font>

138
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:56,320
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#fcfdfc"><b><font face="Times New Roman">Earth</font></b></font></font>

139
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With Luthier's growth, the plus 
on my fire stat has gone up.</i></font>

140
00:09:55,290 --> 00:09:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And...</i></font>

141
00:09:56,610 --> 00:09:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zoey.</font>

142
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

143
00:09:59,210 --> 00:10:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}By the power of the spirits with 
whom I have forged a pact,</font>

144
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:02,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the six years since I hired her,</i></font>

145
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}tell me this individual's 
intentions and disposition.</font>

146
00:10:02,690 --> 00:10:07,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Zoey has learned many skills to repay 
the debt she feels she owes me.</i></font>

147
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It went up.</font>

148
00:10:09,770 --> 00:10:12,750
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="40"><font color="#f5fcff">Level</font></font></font></b></font>

149
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing! You didn't even 
have to do any fighting!</font>

150
00:10:15,820 --> 00:10:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never heard of anything like this!</font>

151
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the result of 
making my dolls battle.</font>

152
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:25,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-So if you keep making them fight, 
will it keep going up forever?</font>

153
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It isn't that simple.</font>

154
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To raise it from Level 1 to 2 
took only one battle,</font>

155
00:10:31,560 --> 00:10:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but to raise it from 2 to 3, I had 
to make them fight over ten times.</font>

156
00:10:36,650 --> 00:10:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think fighting the same opponent 
every time is inefficient.</font>

157
00:10:40,500 --> 00:10:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I see.</font>

158
00:10:43,350 --> 00:10:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I want to learn how it 
works in better detail,</font>

159
00:10:45,860 --> 00:10:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll need to collect even 
more magic items like these.</font>

160
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that sounds interesting.</font>

161
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:59,320
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#efefeb">Henry Ararat 
<font size="13">Minister-Prince of Military Affairs, Fourth Prince</font></font></b></font>

162
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother.</font>

163
00:11:02,230 --> 00:11:04,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Making your magic sword battle your ring?</font>

164
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the inventiveness I expect of you.</font>

165
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where were you watching from?</font>

166
00:11:15,190 --> 00:11:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The monster nest has finally matured.</font>

167
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for your first campaign.</font>

168
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The monster nest...</i></font>

169
00:11:23,290 --> 00:11:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A hunting ground managed by the 
Ministry of Military Affairs</i></font>

170
00:11:26,450 --> 00:11:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>for the purpose of serving as 
every prince's first campaign.</i></font>

171
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you open this box,</font>

172
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it'll give a reading of how many soldiers 
you should take on your first campaign.</font>

173
00:11:35,690 --> 00:11:37,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have a system for that?</font>

174
00:11:37,630 --> 00:11:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't want too many or too 
few for this sort of thing.</font>

175
00:11:41,290 --> 00:11:42,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on, open it.</font>

176
00:11:50,260 --> 00:11:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One?</font>

177
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean I alone am sufficient?</font>

178
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:58,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe it... 
This is unprecedented.</font>

179
00:12:01,070 --> 00:12:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really are amazing, you know that?</font>

180
00:12:06,610 --> 00:12:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me.</font>

181
00:12:10,680 --> 00:12:12,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a visitor.</font>

182
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He says he brings orders 
from His Majesty.</font>

183
00:12:17,460 --> 00:12:18,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let him in.</font>

184
00:12:19,300 --> 00:12:22,920
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#fffefa">Reiss Keiki 
<font size="12">Direct Subordinate of the Fourth Prince</font></font></b></font>

185
00:12:20,050 --> 00:12:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emperor's orders.</font>

186
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

187
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone who delivers a personal order</i></font>

188
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>from the emperor can be
considered his proxy.</i></font>

189
00:12:29,150 --> 00:12:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He must be shown the same courtesy 
as the emperor in every aspect.</i></font>

190
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wise Prince Noah Ararat's first 
campaign will be postponed.</font>

191
00:12:38,310 --> 00:12:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stand by until you 
receive further orders.</font>

192
00:12:40,490 --> 00:12:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

193
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:46,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is good to see you 
again, Your Highness.</font>

194
00:12:47,810 --> 00:12:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Reiss. You are 
part of Henry's household.</font>

195
00:12:52,690 --> 00:12:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am.</font>

196
00:12:54,210 --> 00:12:56,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Members of the imperial family</i></font>

197
00:12:56,180 --> 00:13:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>sometimes send one of their slaves or 
servants away to serve as officials.</i></font>

198
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:03,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those of such origins are considered</i></font>

199
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>members of that noble's family who have 
been discharged from their service.</i></font>

200
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They are considered government officials
and subordinates of the imperial family.</i></font>

201
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:20,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413b2b"><font size="15">Noah</font></font></font></font>

202
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:20,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413b2b"><font size="15">Henry</font></font></font></font>

203
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:20,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#2f2412"><font size="15">Imperial Family</font></font></font></font>

204
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:20,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413b2b"><font size="10">Household
Member</font></font></font></b></font>

205
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:20,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413b2b"><font size="10">Subordinate</font></font></font></b></font>

206
00:13:12,970 --> 00:13:20,770
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#413b2b">Reiss</font></font></font></font>

207
00:13:13,710 --> 00:13:16,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The imperial household members who 
work in service to each prince</i></font>

208
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:19,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>have the strictest etiquette 
standards imposed on them.</i></font>

209
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why has it been postponed?</font>

210
00:13:23,770 --> 00:13:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Entirely because of your strength.</font>

211
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:30,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The emperor was so delighted 
by the unprecedented reading,</font>

212
00:13:30,090 --> 00:13:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he said it should be 
carried out on a grand scale.</font>

213
00:13:33,650 --> 00:13:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that explains it.</font>

214
00:13:35,860 --> 00:13:40,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty is currently working with 
Prince Henry and the Eighth Prince</font>

215
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to come up with a way to share how 
remarkable you are with the whole empire.</font>

216
00:13:45,230 --> 00:13:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I guess my first campaign 
won't happen for a while.</font>

217
00:13:49,170 --> 00:13:52,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic items that possess their own will?</font>

218
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

219
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:55,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything will suffice.</font>

220
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something like a cursed doll,
for example.</font>

221
00:13:57,800 --> 00:14:01,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm terribly sorry.
I don't have anything like that.</font>

222
00:14:01,570 --> 00:14:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

223
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I didn't expect to 
find more right away.</font>

224
00:14:06,230 --> 00:14:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shirley, if you please.</font>

225
00:14:08,290 --> 00:14:09,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right.</font>

226
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this.</font>

227
00:14:12,770 --> 00:14:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you come across anything that 
might fit the bill, contact me.</font>

228
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:17,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But... I can't accept that!</font>

229
00:14:17,660 --> 00:14:22,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and of course, I'll reward you 
again if you find anything good.</font>

230
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm counting on you.</font>

231
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you so much!</font>

232
00:14:32,050 --> 00:14:33,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

233
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very sorry.</font>

234
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:39,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just can't believe you paid him so 
much when he didn't have anything.</font>

235
00:14:39,440 --> 00:14:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how nobles shop.</font>

236
00:14:40,830 --> 00:14:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Do you even know who I am?!</font>

237
00:14:44,120 --> 00:14:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say that again if you think you can!</font>

238
00:14:46,570 --> 00:14:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you say?!</font>

239
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said that another customer has 
already reserved that item...</font>

240
00:14:52,310 --> 00:14:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm telling you that <i>I'll</i> buy it!</font>

241
00:14:58,280 --> 00:15:00,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what's with those looks?</font>

242
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:03,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys all do business 
here too, don't you?</font>

243
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:06,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to lose your deals with us?!</font>

244
00:15:06,270 --> 00:15:07,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop.</font>

245
00:15:08,410 --> 00:15:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! Who the hell are—</font>

246
00:15:12,140 --> 00:15:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, if it isn't Prince Noah!</font>

247
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:17,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know me?</font>

248
00:15:17,260 --> 00:15:18,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow me to introduce myself.</font>

249
00:15:18,950 --> 00:15:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am a member of
Prince Gilbert's household.</font>

250
00:15:21,380 --> 00:15:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Dalem.</font>

251
00:15:23,800 --> 00:15:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I once saw you at the Ministry 
of the Imperial Household.</font>

252
00:15:27,210 --> 00:15:29,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And why is a man like you doing this?</font>

253
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was intimidation.</font>

254
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this now?</font>

255
00:15:32,980 --> 00:15:37,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are the minister-prince of 
justice, and you don't know?</font>

256
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:40,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those in the Ministry of the Imperial 
Household can't be found guilty</font>

257
00:15:40,750 --> 00:15:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of any crimes other than insurrection 
or assisting an enemy.</font>

258
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am quite familiar with 
imperial law myself.</font>

259
00:15:47,150 --> 00:15:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I would rather you 
didn't say anything to me,</font>

260
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no matter how trifling it may be.</font>

261
00:15:55,650 --> 00:15:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Noah?</font>

262
00:15:57,140 --> 00:16:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Servants of the imperial family,
especially princes,</i></font>

263
00:16:00,610 --> 00:16:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>already enjoy quite high status.</i></font>

264
00:16:02,830 --> 00:16:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And he's a member of the 
First Prince's household</i></font>

265
00:16:05,180 --> 00:16:07,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i></i>and<i> the Ministry of the 
Imperial Household.</i></font>

266
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's privileged enough that his 
attitude isn't surprising.</i></font>

267
00:16:11,730 --> 00:16:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand clearly.</font>

268
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:14,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

269
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:17,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But? But what?</font>

270
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:20,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you are a member 
of my brother's household.</font>

271
00:16:20,990 --> 00:16:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If so, why are you standing up 
straight when you look at me?</font>

272
00:16:25,980 --> 00:16:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's the same as when 
I saw Reiss yesterday.</i></font>

273
00:16:28,690 --> 00:16:32,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Based on our positions, Dalem 
should be showing respect to me.</i></font>

274
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I didn't realize—</font>

275
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:36,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too late. Apprehend him, Shirley!</font>

276
00:16:36,120 --> 00:16:36,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right away!</font>

277
00:16:44,190 --> 00:16:46,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I am Prince Gilbert's...</font>

278
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence.</font>

279
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still don't understand that 
you've tarnished my brother's name?</font>

280
00:16:52,110 --> 00:16:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dalem, part of the First 
Prince's household,</font>

281
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:56,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has behaved rudely toward 
the Thirteenth Prince.</font>

282
00:16:57,350 --> 00:16:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He will be punished under internal law.</font>

283
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who has a whip?</font>

284
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do!</font>

285
00:17:03,490 --> 00:17:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you people just watching?!</font>

286
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll regret this, damn it!
I swear you will!</font>

287
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:11,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure you pay!</font>

288
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am of the Ministry of 
the Imperial Household!</font>

289
00:17:13,890 --> 00:17:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many lashes?</font>

290
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, let's see...</font>

291
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you or one of my household</font>

292
00:17:19,010 --> 00:17:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">tyrannized my people under the
mantle of borrowed authority,</font>

293
00:17:22,390 --> 00:17:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't hesitate to 
sentence you to death.</font>

294
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:29,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

295
00:17:30,430 --> 00:17:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Your Highness! Please forgive me!</font>

296
00:17:31,730 --> 00:17:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Serves you right!</font>

297
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please forgive me, Your Highness!</font>

298
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All you ever did was throw your 
weight around to screw us over!</font>

299
00:17:36,870 --> 00:17:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness!</font>

300
00:17:47,390 --> 00:17:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has breathed his last.</font>

301
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Has law enforcement arrived?</font>

302
00:17:52,970 --> 00:17:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

303
00:17:53,940 --> 00:17:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once all is taken care of, 
have them write a report</font>

304
00:17:56,780 --> 00:17:58,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with the charges I described earlier.</font>

305
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

306
00:18:00,210 --> 00:18:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, get me a set of handcuffs.</font>

307
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

308
00:18:09,760 --> 00:18:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, if it isn't the Thirteenth Prince...</font>

309
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

310
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've come to apologize to my brother.</font>

311
00:18:16,870 --> 00:18:18,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you tell him that, please?</font>

312
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let him in.</font>

313
00:18:23,580 --> 00:18:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is that man?</font>

314
00:18:24,970 --> 00:18:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His butler, Coil.</font>

315
00:18:27,360 --> 00:18:30,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please enter. Prince Gilbert awaits.</font>

316
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:37,920
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Episode 8</font></b></font></font>

317
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:37,920
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">The First Versus the Thirteenth</font></b></font></font>

318
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Well, there was no 
other way to handle it.</font>

319
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A mere member of my household dared 
to disparage an imperial prince.</font>

320
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:49,850
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#fbfbf7">Gilbert Ararat 
<font size="13">First Prince</font></font></b></font>

321
00:18:49,100 --> 00:18:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He deserved death.</font>

322
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:55,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, I should have 
consulted with you first.</font>

323
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:57,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sincerely apologize.</font>

324
00:18:58,680 --> 00:19:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... Dalem... Dalem, you say?</font>

325
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't remember that name.</font>

326
00:19:04,820 --> 00:19:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I may...</font>

327
00:19:06,370 --> 00:19:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He relocated to the Ministry of the 
Imperial Household a few years ago.</font>

328
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right, him.</font>

329
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All the more reason not 
to fret over this.</font>

330
00:19:15,040 --> 00:19:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fired him and sent him 
away for misconduct.</font>

331
00:19:19,680 --> 00:19:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He couldn't even be called 
a member of my household.</font>

332
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:23,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. So that's it.</i></font>

333
00:19:28,470 --> 00:19:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In fact, I would even go so far as 
to say you protected my reputation.</font>

334
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Had he been left to his 
own devices any longer,</font>

335
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he would have continued to carry 
out evil deeds in my name.</font>

336
00:19:42,190 --> 00:19:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, dear brother.</font>

337
00:19:45,290 --> 00:19:50,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can see why His Majesty 
named you the keeper of the law.</font>

338
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most wouldn't have carried out his 
sentence on the spot like that.</font>

339
00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Prince Noah...</font>

340
00:19:59,010 --> 00:20:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was the purpose of that apology?</font>

341
00:20:02,700 --> 00:20:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

342
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:06,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you see...</font>

343
00:20:06,020 --> 00:20:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're asking if it was necessary 
to go see him in handcuffs</font>

344
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when he seemed so nonchalant 
about the whole thing?</font>

345
00:20:12,130 --> 00:20:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Yes, exactly!</font>

346
00:20:14,270 --> 00:20:17,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how he looked, he was furious.</font>

347
00:20:18,060 --> 00:20:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But he couldn't afford to create 
a rift between him and me.</font>

348
00:20:22,540 --> 00:20:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The emperor favors me more than 
him right now, after all.</font>

349
00:20:26,470 --> 00:20:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

350
00:20:28,510 --> 00:20:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the younger brother apologizes 
first after doing something wrong,</font>

351
00:20:32,430 --> 00:20:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">what does the older brother do?</font>

352
00:20:34,300 --> 00:20:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that I can understand!</font>

353
00:20:37,010 --> 00:20:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can't get mad if the younger 
brother apologizes first.</font>

354
00:20:40,430 --> 00:20:45,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention my brother disavowed Dalem
and the slave traders with such ease.</font>

355
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'd done nothing, I'd become 
a target for harassment.</font>

356
00:20:51,230 --> 00:20:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behind the curtain,
he sees me as an enemy.</font>

357
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I apologized, and he accepted it.</font>

358
00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Among nobles, rehashing a problem
previously apologized for is unseemly.</font>

359
00:21:04,290 --> 00:21:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gave it <i>that</i> much thought?</font>

360
00:21:07,120 --> 00:21:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible!</font>

361
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prince Noah, you have a visitor.</font>

362
00:21:13,030 --> 00:21:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one showing 
them in? How unusual.</font>

363
00:21:16,640 --> 00:21:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He says he's from the Ministry 
of the Imperial Household.</font>

364
00:21:19,860 --> 00:21:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

365
00:21:22,360 --> 00:21:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an honor to meet you.</font>

366
00:21:24,340 --> 00:21:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Don Orts.</font>

367
00:21:27,340 --> 00:21:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want?</font>

368
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was deeply impressed by how you 
handled yesterday's incident.</font>

369
00:21:33,570 --> 00:21:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have come to ask that you allow 
me to work under you as well.</font>

370
00:21:39,710 --> 00:21:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me? But our jurisdictions are different.</font>

371
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A member of the Ministry of the Imperial
Household would struggle here.</font>

372
00:21:47,300 --> 00:21:48,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind.</font>

373
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can simply use me 
whenever you have the need.</font>

374
00:21:53,360 --> 00:21:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

375
00:21:55,970 --> 00:21:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

376
00:22:03,090 --> 00:22:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dylan.</font>

377
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:04,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

378
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look into that man.</font>

379
00:22:07,970 --> 00:22:09,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And be thorough about it.</font>

